    <div style="basic">
        <p begin="00:00:00.400" end="00:00:03.340" tts:direction="ltr">Hello, visitors. For this AG,</p>
        <p begin="00:00:03.340" end="00:00:07.640" tts:direction="ltr">I'm going to talk a little bit about how
<br />to design your data and tableau.</p>
        <p begin="00:00:07.640" end="00:00:11.660" tts:direction="ltr">We will have a base camp that will cover
<br />design principles,</p>
        <p begin="00:00:11.660" end="00:00:14.480" tts:direction="ltr">and I'm sure that along your adventure,</p>
        <p begin="00:00:14.480" end="00:00:18.540" tts:direction="ltr">you've already been working with some of
<br />the design features in Tableau.</p>
        <p begin="00:00:18.540" end="00:00:20.180" tts:direction="ltr">I will just review some of</p>
        <p begin="00:00:20.180" end="00:00:23.440" tts:direction="ltr">the formatting on a worksheet level, the
<br />field level.</p>
        <p begin="00:00:23.440" end="00:00:25.800" tts:direction="ltr">I'll talk about how you can add shapes and</p>
        <p begin="00:00:25.800" end="00:00:29.520" tts:direction="ltr">custom color and then round it off with
<br />some accessibility.</p>
        <p begin="00:00:29.520" end="00:00:35.320" tts:direction="ltr">Again, we'll be talking more in detail
<br />about design in the next base camp.</p>
        <p begin="00:00:35.320" end="00:00:39.420" tts:direction="ltr">I would like for you to hop into the
<br />adventure guide,</p>
        <p begin="00:00:39.420" end="00:00:42.780" tts:direction="ltr">which is the Tau AG design start.</p>
        <p begin="00:00:42.780" end="00:00:47.305" tts:direction="ltr">The very first screen, I've got an
<br />overview of a before and after dashboard.</p>
        <p begin="00:00:47.305" end="00:00:50.810" tts:direction="ltr">Now, both of these dashboards have been
<br />designed.</p>
