        <p begin="00:00:53.190" end="00:00:58.510" tts:direction="ltr">a little more intentionality for that user
<br />to try to simplify that story.</p>
        <p begin="00:00:58.510" end="00:01:01.330" tts:direction="ltr">There's a lot of complexity and
<br />dashboards,</p>
        <p begin="00:01:01.330" end="00:01:05.130" tts:direction="ltr">and I just want you to keep this in mind
