        <p begin="00:01:11.280" end="00:01:13.100" tts:direction="ltr">who your audience is.</p>
        <p begin="00:01:13.100" end="00:01:17.320" tts:direction="ltr">Do you have a message that needs to be
<br />pulled</p>
        <p begin="00:01:17.320" end="00:01:23.040" tts:direction="ltr">out that there might be a mood that you're
<br />trying to convey.</p>
        <p begin="00:01:23.040" end="00:01:26.480" tts:direction="ltr">Of course, there needs to be that idea of
<br />consistency.</p>
