        <p begin="00:03:20.920" end="00:03:23.020" tts:direction="ltr">If I'm able to select this,</p>
        <p begin="00:03:23.020" end="00:03:25.980" tts:direction="ltr">the relationship will change accordingly.</p>
        <p begin="00:03:25.980" end="00:03:29.860" tts:direction="ltr">Don't ever make the mistake of having
<br />peach here and</p>
        <p begin="00:03:29.860" end="00:03:33.920" tts:direction="ltr">then peach here and peach here with
<br />different variables.</p>
        <p begin="00:03:33.920" end="00:03:37.220" tts:direction="ltr">That will very much confuse your audience.</p>
        <p begin="00:03:37.220" end="00:03:41.380" tts:direction="ltr">You also see here that the tiled map</p>
        <p begin="00:03:41.380" end="00:03:46.380" tts:direction="ltr">has been converted to a gray scale to
